---
import SectionHeader from './SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="relative">
  <SectionHeader
    index="04"
    label="About"
    title="Engineer first, business translator always."
    kicker="Background."
  />

  <div class="max-w-page mx-auto px-5 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-7 fade-up">
        <div class="card p-5 md:p-6">
          <p class="text-[15px] md:text-base leading-relaxed text-ink">
            Licensed Electronics Engineer who wandered into Data &amp; AI,
            and stayed. 8+ years across academia, R&amp;D, and industry.
            Most recently leading data engineering and data science teams
            before going independent in late 2023.
          </p>
          <p
            class="mt-4 text-[14px] md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted"
          >
            Contract work has spanned AI &amp; ML engineering for AU
            software consulting, data engineering for a UK Airbnb revenue
            firm, and marketing analytics for US clients across airline,
            eCommerce, on-demand delivery, and investment management.
            Across the stack: production data engineering (dbt, Airflow,
            Snowflake, Databricks, DuckDB), applied AI (agents, RAG,
            evaluation, LangChain / LangGraph), and research in computer
            vision and robotics (IEEE-published).
          </p>
          <p
            class="mt-4 text-[14px] md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted"
          >
            I care about systems that survive contact with real data, real
            users, and real deadlines. Explainable on a napkin, debuggable
            at 2&nbsp;a.m.
          </p>
          <p
            class="mt-4 text-[14px] md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-muted"
          >
            Outside client work, I write on Medium, guest in YouTube tutorial
            channels about data careers, and publish free Notion roadmaps
            for people trying to find their way in, because the path I took
            was poorly documented, and I'd like that to be less true for
            everyone else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-5 fade-up">
        <div class="card p-5 md:p-6">
          <p class="mono-label">Timeline</p>
          <ul
            class="mt-4 divide-y divide-border font-mono text-[12.5px] leading-relaxed"
          >
            <li class="flex gap-4 py-2.5">
              <span class="text-subtle w-14 shrink-0">NOW</span>
              <span class="text-ink">Freelance Data &amp; AI/ML Engineer, Manila.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 py-2.5">
              <span class="text-subtle w-14 shrink-0">CLIENTS</span>
              <span class="text-ink">AU, UK, US, CA firms across software, real estate, marketing, eCom.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 py-2.5">
              <span class="text-subtle w-14 shrink-0">LED</span>
              <span class="text-ink">DE &amp; DS teams at a PH tech firm (2022–2023).</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 py-2.5">
              <span class="text-subtle w-14 shrink-0">PAST</span>
              <span class="text-ink">AI researcher &amp; DLSU lecturer; IEEE-published in CV &amp; robotics.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4 py-2.5">
              <span class="text-subtle w-14 shrink-0">NEXT</span>
              <span class="text-ink">Help you scale your business with data &amp; AI solutions.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 card p-5 md:p-6">
          <p class="mono-label">Free resources</p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-[13.5px]">
            <li>
              <a
                href="https://shadow-blue-572.notion.site/c3f88e41209349f6a0a18c40684a420a"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="group flex items-start justify-between gap-3 text-ink hover:text-accent transition"
              >
                <span class="flex-1">Data Analyst Roadmap</span>
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-subtle group-hover:text-accent transition" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"></path></svg>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a
                href="https://shadow-blue-572.notion.site/b880b4ef0b1445aabec127442b97c79f?v=0a45fb3e2b5946d59708797eeea16671"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noreferrer"
                class="group flex items-start justify-between gap-3 text-ink hover:text-accent transition"
              >
                <span class="flex-1">Data Engineer Roadmap</span>
                <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-subtle group-hover:text-accent transition" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M9 7h8v8"></path></svg>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
